snippet.title: Story Epic Tale of Hope Within Despair｜Mad World - Age of Darkness - MMORPG
snippet.description:
Mad World Official Launch on April 27th (Thur)
✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com

[Main story] Mad World offers a glimpse of hope among the overwhelming despair.
[Sub story] Explore a world filled with fear and despair.
[Adventure journal] Create your own story in Mad World's vast world.

=====================================
We have reached 500 thousand pre-registrators!
Now let’s go for 1 million!

Pre-register now if you have not taken part in our pre-registration events yet!

✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com
=====================================
✨MadWorld official site
👉Discord: https://discord.gg/madworldmmo
